They communicated with the Associated Press Agency on condition of anonymity, as they are not authorized to discuss the situation of PSG.
According to the latest published reports, in 2015-1016, PSG received more than 10 million euros in profits with a turnover of 542.4 million euros.
Reporting for the last financial year has not yet been published.
